      • newFile

        public static EstherFile newFile(String name,
                 String type,
                 Long ownerId,
                 Boolean published,
                 Long size,
                 Boolean blocked)
        Returns a new file with the specified attributes.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the file.
        type - The extension of the file.
        ownerId - The ID of the User who owns the file.
        published - Whether the file is public for the other users.
        size - Size of the file in bytes.
        blocked - Whether the file is visible and accessible.
        Returns:
        The created EstherFile.
